          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "This structure holds the value of an animatable property",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "(",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/BindableValue/animatedValue",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": "), that is, the target property that",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "animates. In addition, the structure stores the property’s original value",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "(",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/BindableValue/baseValue",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": "), which represents the property’s value before",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "a running animation starts. The ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/BindableValue/value",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " property returns the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "animated value when an animation runs; when the animation isn’t running, it",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "returns the base value.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
